<div class="tag">
<a href="/shiwen/default.aspx?tstr=%e4%b9%90%e5%ba%9c">乐府</a>
<span>，</span><a href="/shiwen/default.aspx?tstr=%e5%94%90%e8%af%97%e4%b8%89%e7%99%be%e9%a6%96">唐诗三百首</a>
<span>，</span><a href="/shiwen/default.aspx?tstr=%e5%92%8f%e7%89%a9">咏物</a>
<span>，</span><a href="/shiwen/default.aspx?tstr=%e6%8a%92%e6%83%85">抒情</a>
<span>，</span><a href="/shiwen/default.aspx?tstr=%e5%93%b2%e7%90%86">哲理</a>
<span>，</span><a href="/shiwen/default.aspx?tstr=%e5%ae%b4%e9%a5%ae">宴饮</a>
