<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="http://so.gushiwen.org/shiwenv_6c1ea9b7dd44.aspx" target="_blank"><b>陋室铭</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%94%90%e4%bb%a3">唐代</a><span>：</span><a href="http://so.gushiwen.org/search.aspx?value=%e5%88%98%e7%a6%b9%e9%94%a1">刘禹锡</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson71138">
山不在高，有仙则名。水不在深，有龙则灵。斯是陋室，惟吾德馨。苔痕上阶绿，草色入帘青。谈笑有鸿儒，往来无白丁。可以调素琴，阅金经。无丝竹之乱耳，无案牍之劳形。南阳诸葛庐，西蜀子云亭。孔子云：何陋之有？
