<span>，</span><a href="/shiwen/default.aspx?tstr=%e8%8e%b2%e8%8a%b1">莲花</a>
<span>，</span><a href="/shiwen/default.aspx?tstr=%e5%93%81%e6%a0%bc">品格</a>
