<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="http://so.gushiwen.org/shiwenv_a167901c9c90.aspx" target="_blank"><b>元日</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%ae%8b%e4%bb%a3">宋代</a><span>：</span><a href="http://so.gushiwen.org/search.aspx?value=%e7%8e%8b%e5%ae%89%e7%9f%b3">王安石</a></p>
