<div class="tag">
<a href="/shiwen/default.aspx?tstr=%e5%8f%a4%e8%af%97%e4%b8%89%e7%99%be%e9%a6%96">古诗三百首</a>
<span>，</span><a href="/shiwen/default.aspx?tstr=%e5%b0%8f%e5%ad%a6%e5%8f%a4%e8%af%97">小学古诗</a>
<span>，</span><a href="/shiwen/default.aspx?tstr=%e6%98%a5%e8%8a%82">春节</a>
<span>，</span><a href="/shiwen/default.aspx?tstr=%e9%a3%8e%e4%bf%97">风俗</a>
<span>，</span><a href="/shiwen/default.aspx?tstr=%e6%8a%b1%e8%b4%9f">抱负</a>
</div>
