<span>，</span><a href="/shiwen/default.aspx?tstr=%e5%8f%99%e4%ba%8b">叙事</a>
<span>，</span><a href="/shiwen/default.aspx?tstr=%e6%b0%91%e6%ad%8c">民歌</a>
